@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nGET /api/transactions/blockchain/recent" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Transaction" as DB
User->UI: Open the blockchain explorer page
UI->API: Request recent blockchain transactions
API->DB: Retrieve transactions with txHash
DB-->API: Return blockchain transaction data
API-->UI: Return recent blockchain transactions
UI-->User: Display blockchain transaction details

@enduml
